Knox Matrix monitors supported devices signed in to your Samsung account using a secure private blockchain. Each device in the chain can check the security status of other devices and let you know if there are any threats.

"The security status of this phone hasn't been updated for more than 30 days. The phone may be offline or something may be preventing its status from being checked. If you aren't using this phone anymore, signing out of your Samsung account is recommended. You can sign out in Settings > Samsung account > Devices.
If you're using this phone but its security status isn't updating, make sure it's connected to a network."
